<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٩٧١ - وَعِدَّةٌ مِنَ الصِّحَابِ وَصَلُوا … عِشْرِينَ بَعْدَ مِئَةٍ تُكَمَّلُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٩٧٢ -<span style="color:#006d98"> سِتُّونَ فِي الْإِسْلَامِ:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«حَسَّانٌ»</span>، يَلِي … <span style="color:#6c6c00">«حُوَيْطِبٌ»</span>، <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مَخْرَمَةُ بْنُ نَوْفَلِ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٩٧٣ - ثُمَّ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«حَكِيمٌ»</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«حَمْنَنٌ»</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«سَعِيدُ»</span> … وَآخَرُونَ مُطْلَقاً: <span style="color:#6c6c00">«لَبِيدُ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٩٧٤ - <span style="color:#6c6c00">«عَاصِمُ»</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«سَعْدٌ»</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«نَوْفَلٌ»</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مُنْتَجِعُ»</span> … <span style="color:#6c6c00">«لَجْلَاجُ»</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«أَوْسٌ»</span> وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«عَدِيٌّ»</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«نَافِعُ»</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٩٧٥ - <span style="color:#6c6c00">«نَابِغَةٌ»</span>، ثُمَّةَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«حَسَّانُ»</span> انْفَرَدْ … أَنْ عَاشَ ذَا أَبٌ وَجَدُّهُ وَجَدّْ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٩٧٦ - ثُمَّ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«حَكِيمٌ»</span> مُفْرَدٌ بَأَنْ وُلِدْ … بِكَعْبَةٍ؛ وَمَا لِغَيْرِهِ عُهِدْ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٩٧٧ - وَمَاتَ مَعْ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«حَسَّانَ»</span> عَامَ أَرْبَعِ … مِنْ بَعْدِ خَمْسِينَ عَلَى تَنَازُعِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٩٧٨ - لِمِئَةٍ وَنِصْفِهَا <span style="color:#6c6c00">«النُّعْمَانُ»</span> … وَبَعْدَ إِحْدَى عَشْرَةٍ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«سُفْيَانُ»</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٩٧٩ - وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مَالِكٌ»</span> فِي التِّسْعِ وَالسَّبْعِينَا … وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«الشَّافِعِي»</span> الْأَرْبَعُ مَعْ قَرْنَيْنَا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٩٨٠ - وَفِي ثَمَانٍ وَثَلَاثِينَ قَضَى … <span style="color:#6c6c00">«إِسْحَاقُ»</span>، بَعْدَ أَرْبَعِينَ قَدْ مَضَى<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>